		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Josh Weil</span></strong> is the author of the book of novellas <em>The New Valley</em>, which won the Sue Kaufman Prize for First Fiction and a &ldquo;5 Under 35&rdquo; award from the National Book Foundation. His next novel, <em>The Great Glass Sea</em>, will be published in 2014. He lives with his girlfriend and her daughter in two side-by-side wood-heated cabins in Nevada City, California.</p><a href="/contributors/josh-weil" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
